ActJudges Act (Removal Allowance) Order
PrecisOrder prescribing an additional period during which certain RELOCATION EXPENSES may be reimbursed to The Hon. CLAUDE AUCLAIR who was required to relocate following his appointment as a Puisne Judge of the Superior Court for the District of Montréal in the Province of Quebec on September 24, 2004.
